{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"63416e57d6","title":"关于同意目前收兵休整致彭德怀电","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"caa3ea36a5","index":0,"year":1951,"month":5,"day":22,"articleId":"63416e57d6"}],"tags":[{"id":"ae0a6697a5","name":"彭德怀","type":"人物"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji30","name":"毛泽东全集第30卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/30-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji30":{"comments":[{"id":"f92d9b1e37","publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"63416e57d6","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"彭德怀，当时任中国人民志愿军司令员兼政治委员。"},{"id":"c1011db51e","publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"63416e57d6","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"高岗，当时任中国人民解放军东北军区司令员兼政治委员。"},{"id":"efd08e90fc","publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"63416e57d6","index":3,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"指彭德怀1951年5月21日23时给毛泽东的电报。电报说：第五次战役为时一个月，进行东西两线作战，部队有些疲劳，需恢复和总结战斗经验。战斗发起后，第一线运输极端困难，且雨季已接近开始，数江湖沼尽在我军之后，一旦山洪暴发，交通全断，顾虑甚大。此役未消灭美师团建制，故夸大我之伤亡，还有北犯可能。根据上述，我军继续前进，不易消灭敌人，徒增困难，不如后撤，使主力休整，寻机开敌。"}],"contents":[{"id":"c4589732c4","type":"title","text":"关于同意日前收兵休整致彭德怀电","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"63416e57d6"},{"id":"f92d9b1e37","type":"paragraph","text":"德怀同志，并告高岗同志：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"63416e57d6"},{"id":"c1011db51e","type":"paragraph","text":"廿一日廿三时电以悉。根据自前情况收兵休整，准备再战，这个处置是正确的。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"63416e57d6"},{"id":"efd08e90fc","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"63416e57d6"},{"id":"9a47e6c929","type":"paragraph","text":"五月二十二日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"63416e57d6"}],"page":{"id":"224774d220","publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"63416e57d6","start":323,"end":323}}}},"__N_SSG":true}